text: Leng Ngeth (; 1900 – 1975) was Prime Minister of Cambodia from January to October 1955.http://rulers.org/rulc1.html From 1958 to 1962 he was Ambassador in Beijing. ==References== Category:1900 births Category:1975 deaths Category:20th-century Cambodian politicians Category:Cambodian diplomats Category:People executed by the Khmer Rouge Category:Democratic Party (Cambodia) politicians Category:Prime Ministers of Cambodia Category:People from Phnom Penh Category:Ambassadors of Cambodia to China
